Heather Hughes Appointed Interim Dean of AUWCL

Dean Hughes to Start July 1

Read more

Nationally Ranked Specialty Programs

American University Washington College of Law’s top specialty programs, nationally ranked by U.S. News and World Report – #1 Clinical Program (tie); #5 International Law; #7 Intellectual Property; #16 Health Care Law; #16 Part-Time; – are just a few of our nationally recognized areas of excellence. We provide our students with the critical skills and values to have an immediate impact in the Washington, D.C. region, our nation, and around the world.
